<HL>
   Riegle, Seeking Political Advantage,
   Paints Gloomy Picture of S&amp;L Cleanup
   ----
   By Paulette Thomas
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/12/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A6
</SO>
<IN>
